{"atom_id": "ig34_p0010_a015", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 10, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§1.4.1 [How to Read a Domain Specification]", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "Examples of values that might appear in the variable. Such examples are only examples, and although they may be CDISC Controlled Terminology values, their presence in a CDISC Note should not be construed as definitive. For authoritative information on CDISC Controlled Terminology, consult https://www.cancer.gov/research/resources/terminology/cdisc.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2", "ts": "2026-04-24T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0010_a016", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 10, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§1.4.1 [How to Read a Domain Specification]", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "Core: Contains 1 of the 3 values—\"Req\", \"Exp\", or \"Perm\"—explained further in Section 4.1.5, SDTM Core Designations.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": ["§4.1.5 SDTM Core Designations"], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2", "ts": "2026-04-24T00:00:00Z"}}
