{"atom_id": "ig34_p0012_a003", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 12, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§2.2 Datasets and Domains", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "All datasets are structured as flat files with rows representing observations and columns representing variables.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch02_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-24T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0012_a004", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 12, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§2.2 Datasets and Domains", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Each dataset is described by metadata definitions that provide information about the variables used in the dataset.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch02_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-24T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0012_a005", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 12, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§2.2 Datasets and Domains", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "The metadata are described in a data definition document (i.e., a Define-XML document) that is submitted with the data to regulatory authorities.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch02_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-24T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0012_a006", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 12, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§2.2 Datasets and Domains", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "The Define-XML standard (available at https://www.cdisc.org/standards/data-exchange/define-xml) specifies metadata attributes to describe SDTM data.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch02_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-24T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0012_a007", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 12, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§2.2 Datasets and Domains", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Data represented in SDTM datasets include data as originally collected or received, data from the protocol, assigned data, and derived data.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch02_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-24T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0012_a008", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 12, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§2.2 Datasets and Domains", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "The SDTM lists only the name, label, and type, with a set of brief CDISC guidelines that provide a general description for each variable.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch02_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-24T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0012_a009", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 12, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§2.2 Datasets and Domains", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "The domain dataset models in Section 5, Models for Special-purpose Domains, and Section 6, Domain Models Based on the General Observation Classes, provide additional information about controlled terms or format, notes on proper usage, and examples.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": ["§5", "§6"], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch02_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-24T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0012_a010", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 12, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§2.2 Datasets and Domains", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "See also Section 1.4.1, How to Read a Domain Specification.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": ["§1.4.1"], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch02_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-24T00:00:00Z"}}
