{"atom_id": "ig34_p0016_a022", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 16, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§2.7 SDTM Variables Not Allowed in the SDTMIG", "atom_type": "NOTE", "verbatim": "The use of POOLID additionally requires the use of the Pool Definition dataset.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch02_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-24T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0016_a023", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 16, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "§2.7 SDTM Variables Not Allowed in the SDTMIG", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Other variables defined in the SDTM are allowed for use as defined in this SDTMIG except when explicitly stated.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch02_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-24T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0016_a024", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 16, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "§2.7 SDTM Variables Not Allowed in the SDTMIG", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Custom domains, created following the guidance in Section 2.6, Creating a New Domain, may utilize any appropriate qualifier variables from the selected general observation class.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": ["§2.6"], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch02_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-24T00:00:00Z"}}
