{"atom_id": "ig34_p0026_a020", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 26, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.1.8.1 [Origin Metadata for Variables]", "atom_type": "HEADING", "verbatim": "4.1.8.1  Origin Metadata for Variables", "heading_level": 4, "sibling_index": 1, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch03_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-24T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0026_a021", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 26, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.1.8.1 [Origin Metadata for Variables]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "The origin element in the Define-XML document file is used to indicate where the data originated.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch03_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-24T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0026_a022", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 26, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.1.8.1 [Origin Metadata for Variables]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Its purpose is to unambiguously communicate to the reviewer the origin of the data source.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch03_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-24T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0026_a023", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 26, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.1.8.1 [Origin Metadata for Variables]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "For example, data could be collected (on the CRF, from a vendor, or from a device), derived, or assigned; CRF data should be traceable to an annotated CRF and derived data should be traceable to some derivation algorithm.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch03_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-24T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0026_a024", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 26, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.1.8.1 [Origin Metadata for Variables]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "The Define-XML specification is the definitive source of allowable origin values.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch03_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-24T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0026_a025", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 26, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.1.8.1 [Origin Metadata for Variables]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Additional guidance and supporting examples can be referenced using the Metadata Submission Guidelines (MSG) for SDTMIG.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch03_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-24T00:00:00Z"}}
