{"atom_id": "ig34_p0032_a009", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 32, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§4.2.7.1 \"Specify\" Values for Non-result Qualifier Variables", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "SUPPEX QNAM = \"EXADJDSC\", QLABEL = \"Reason For Dose Adjustment Description\", QVAL = \"PATIENT MISUNDERSTOOD INSTRUCTIONS\"", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0032_a010", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 32, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§4.2.7.1 \"Specify\" Values for Non-result Qualifier Variables", "atom_type": "CODE_LITERAL", "verbatim": "SUPPEX QNAM = \"EXADJDSC\", QLABEL = \"Reason For Dose Adjustment Description\", QVAL = \"PATIENT MISUNDERSTOOD INSTRUCTIONS\"", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0032_a011", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 32, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§4.2.7.1 \"Specify\" Values for Non-result Qualifier Variables", "atom_type": "NOTE", "verbatim": "Note that QNAM references the \"parent\" variable name with the addition of \"DSC\". Likewise, the label is a modification of the parent variable label.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0032_a012", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 32, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.2.7.1 \"Specify\" Values for Non-result Qualifier Variables", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "When the CRF includes a list of values for a qualifier field that includes \"Other\" and the \"Other\" is supplemented with a \"Specify\" free-text field, then the manner in which the free-text \"Specify\" value is submitted will vary based on the sponsor's coding practice and analysis requirements.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0032_a013", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 32, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.2.7.1 \"Specify\" Values for Non-result Qualifier Variables", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "For example, consider a CRF that collects the indication for an analgesic concomitant medication (CMINDC) using a list of prespecified values and an \"Other, specify\" field :", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0032_a014", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 32, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.2.7.1 \"Specify\" Values for Non-result Qualifier Variables", "atom_type": "TABLE_HEADER", "verbatim": "Indication for analgesic | Post-operative pain / Headache / Menstrual pain / Myalgia / Toothache / Other, specify: ___________", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0032_a015", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 32, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.2.7.1 \"Specify\" Values for Non-result Qualifier Variables", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "An investigator has selected \"OTHER\" and specified \"Broken arm\".", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0032_a016", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 32, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.2.7.1 \"Specify\" Values for Non-result Qualifier Variables", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Several options are available for submission of this data:", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0032_a017", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 32, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.2.7.1 \"Specify\" Values for Non-result Qualifier Variables", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "If the sponsor wishes to maintain controlled terminology for the CMINDC field and limit the terminology to the 5 prespecified choices, then the free text is placed in SUPPCM.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0032_a018", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 32, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.2.7.1 \"Specify\" Values for Non-result Qualifier Variables", "atom_type": "TABLE_HEADER", "verbatim": "CMINDC | OTHER", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0032_a019", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 32, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.2.7.1 \"Specify\" Values for Non-result Qualifier Variables", "atom_type": "TABLE_HEADER", "verbatim": "QNAM | QLABEL | QVAL", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0032_a020", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 32, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.2.7.1 \"Specify\" Values for Non-result Qualifier Variables", "atom_type": "TABLE_ROW", "verbatim": "CMINDOTH | Other Indication | BROKEN ARM", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0032_a021", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 32, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.2.7.1 \"Specify\" Values for Non-result Qualifier Variables", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "If the sponsor wishes to maintain controlled terminology for CMINDC but will expand the terminology based on values seen in the \"Other, specify\" field, then the value of CMINDC will reflect the sponsor's coding decision and SUPPCM could be used to store the verbatim text.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0032_a022", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 32, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.2.7.1 \"Specify\" Values for Non-result Qualifier Variables", "atom_type": "TABLE_HEADER", "verbatim": "CMINDC | FRACTURE", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0032_a023", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 32, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.2.7.1 \"Specify\" Values for Non-result Qualifier Variables", "atom_type": "TABLE_HEADER", "verbatim": "QNAM | QLABEL | QVAL", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0032_a024", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 32, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.2.7.1 \"Specify\" Values for Non-result Qualifier Variables", "atom_type": "TABLE_ROW", "verbatim": "CMINDOTH | Other Indication | BROKEN ARM", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0032_a025", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 32, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "§4.2.7.1 \"Specify\" Values for Non-result Qualifier Variables", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Note that the sponsor might choose a different value for CMINDC (e.g., \"BONE FRACTURE\") depending on the sponsor's coding practice and analysis requirements.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0032_a026", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 32, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "§4.2.7.1 \"Specify\" Values for Non-result Qualifier Variables", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "If the sponsor does not require that controlled terminology be maintained and wishes for all responses to be stored in a single variable, then CMINDC will be used and SUPPCM is not required.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
