{"atom_id": "ig34_p0033_a001", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 33, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§4.2.7.2 \"Specify\" Values for Result Qualifier Variables", "atom_type": "HEADING", "verbatim": "4.2.7.2  \"Specify\" Values for Result Qualifier Variables", "heading_level": 3, "sibling_index": 2, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0033_a002", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 33, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§4.2.7.2 \"Specify\" Values for Result Qualifier Variables", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "When the CRF includes a list of values for a result field that includes \"Other\" and the \"Other\" is supplemented with a \"Specify\" free-text field, then the manner in which the free-text \"Specify\" value is submitted will vary based on the sponsor's coding practice and analysis requirements.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0033_a003", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 33, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§4.2.7.2 \"Specify\" Values for Result Qualifier Variables", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "For example, consider a CRF where the sponsor requests the subject's eye color:", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0033_a004", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 33, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§4.2.7.2 \"Specify\" Values for Result Qualifier Variables", "atom_type": "TABLE_HEADER", "verbatim": "Eye Color | Brown / Black / Blue / Green / Other, specify: ___________", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0033_a005", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 33, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§4.2.7.2 \"Specify\" Values for Result Qualifier Variables", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "An investigator has selected \"OTHER\" and specified \"BLUEISH GRAY\".", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0033_a006", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 33, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§4.2.7.2 \"Specify\" Values for Result Qualifier Variables", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "As in the preceding discussion for non-result qualifier values, the sponsor has several options for submission:", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0033_a007", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 33, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§4.2.7.2 \"Specify\" Values for Result Qualifier Variables", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "If the sponsor wishes to maintain controlled terminology in the standard result field and limit the terminology to the 5 prespecified choices, then the free text is placed in --ORRES and the controlled terminology in --STRESC.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
