{"atom_id": "ig34_p0034_a002", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 34, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§4.2.7.3 \"Specify\" Values for Topic Variables", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "\"Other, Specify\" for tests may be handled similarly to Interventions.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0034_a003", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 34, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§4.2.7.3 \"Specify\" Values for Topic Variables", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "--TESTCD and --TEST should be populated with the code and description of the test found in the specified text.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0034_a004", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 34, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§4.2.7.3 \"Specify\" Values for Topic Variables", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "If specific tests are not listed on the CRF and the investigator has the option of writing in tests, then the name of the test would have to be coded to ensure that all --TESTCD and --TEST values are consistent with the test controlled terminology.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0034_a005", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 34, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§4.2.7.3 \"Specify\" Values for Topic Variables", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "For example, a lab CRF collected values for hemoglobin, hematocrit, and \"Other, specify\".", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0034_a006", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 34, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§4.2.7.3 \"Specify\" Values for Topic Variables", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "The value the investigator wrote for \"Other, specify\" was \"Prothrombin time\" with an associated result and units.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0034_a007", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 34, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§4.2.7.3 \"Specify\" Values for Topic Variables", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "The sponsor would submit the controlled terminology for this test:  LBTESTCD would be \"PT\" and LBTEST would be \"Prothrombin Time\", rather than the verbatim term, \"Prothrombin time\" supplied by the investigator.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0034_a008", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 34, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§4.2.7.4 \"Specify\" Values for --OBJ", "atom_type": "HEADING", "verbatim": "4.2.7.4  \"Specify\" Values for --OBJ", "heading_level": 3, "sibling_index": 4, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0034_a009", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 34, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§4.2.7.4 \"Specify\" Values for --OBJ", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "As illustrated in the following figure, when findings are collected about an event or intervention, and the name of the event or intervention is collected in an \"Other, specify\" CRF field, the value in --OBJ variable depends on whether the Findings record has a parent record and whether the \"Other, specify\" value was coded.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": ["§6.4.3"], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0034_a010", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 34, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§4.2.7.4 \"Specify\" Values for --OBJ", "atom_type": "CROSS_REF", "verbatim": "See also Section 6.4.3, Variables Unique to Findings About.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": ["§6.4.3"], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0034_a011", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 34, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.2.7.4 \"Specify\" Values for --OBJ", "atom_type": "HEADING", "verbatim": "Figure. Decision Tree for Populating --OBJ", "heading_level": 5, "sibling_index": 1, "figure_ref": "pdf_p0034+middle", "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0034_a012", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 34, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.2.7.4 \"Specify\" Values for --OBJ", "atom_type": "FIGURE", "verbatim": "[FIGURE: Decision tree with root node 'Findings about data for an event or intervention where the name of the event or intervention was entered as free text'; branches: Topic variable coded? Yes→Parent record exists? Yes→Populate --OBJ with --DECOD; No→Populate --OBJ with topic variable value; No→Name of event or intervention coded? Yes→Populate --OBJ with coded value; No→Populate --OBJ with verbatim value]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": "pdf_p0034+middle", "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0034_a013", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 34, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "§4.2.8 Multiple Values for a Variable", "atom_type": "HEADING", "verbatim": "4.2.8 Multiple Values for a Variable", "heading_level": 2, "sibling_index": 8, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0034_a014", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 34, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "§4.2.8.1 Multiple Values for an Intervention or Event Topic Variable", "atom_type": "HEADING", "verbatim": "4.2.8.1  Multiple Values for an Intervention or Event Topic Variable", "heading_level": 3, "sibling_index": 1, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0034_a015", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 34, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "§4.2.8.1 Multiple Values for an Intervention or Event Topic Variable", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "If multiple values are reported for an intervention or event topic variable (e.g., --TRT in an Interventions general observation-class dataset or --TERM in an Events general observation-class dataset), it is expected that the sponsor will split the values into multiple records or otherwise resolve the multiplicity per the sponsor's data management standard operating procedures.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0034_a016", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 34, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "§4.2.8.1 Multiple Values for an Intervention or Event Topic Variable", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "For example, if an adverse event term of \"Headache and nausea\" or a concomitant medication of \"Tylenol and Benadryl\" is reported, sponsors will often split the original report into separate records and/or query the site for clarification.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0034_a017", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 34, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "§4.2.8.1 Multiple Values for an Intervention or Event Topic Variable", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "By the time of submission, datasets should be in conformance with the record structures described in the SDTMIG.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0034_a018", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 34, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "§4.2.8.1 Multiple Values for an Intervention or Event Topic Variable", "atom_type": "NOTE", "verbatim": "Note: The Disposition (DS) dataset is an exception to the general rule of splitting multiple topic values into separate records.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0034_a019", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 34, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "§4.2.8.1 Multiple Values for an Intervention or Event Topic Variable", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "For DS, 1 record for each disposition or protocol milestone is permitted according to the domain structure.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0034_a020", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 34, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "§4.2.8.1 Multiple Values for an Intervention or Event Topic Variable", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "For cases of multiple reasons for discontinuation see Section 6.2.4, Disposition, assumption 5 for additional information.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": ["§6.2.4"], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
