{"atom_id": "ig34_p0035_a006", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 35, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§4.2.8.2 Multiple Values for a Findings Result Variable", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "When a finding can have multiple results, the key structure for the findings dataset must be adequate to distinguish between the multiple results.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": ["§4.1.9"], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0035_a007", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 35, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§4.2.8.2 Multiple Values for a Findings Result Variable", "atom_type": "CROSS_REF", "verbatim": "See Section 4.1.9, Assigning Natural Keys in the Metadata.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": ["§4.1.9"], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0035_a008", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 35, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§4.2.8.3 Multiple Values for a Non-result Qualifier Variable", "atom_type": "HEADING", "verbatim": "4.2.8.3  Multiple Values for a Non-result Qualifier Variable", "heading_level": 3, "sibling_index": 3, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0035_a009", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 35, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§4.2.8.3 Multiple Values for a Non-result Qualifier Variable", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "The SDTM permits 1 value for each qualifier variable per record.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0035_a010", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 35, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§4.2.8.3 Multiple Values for a Non-result Qualifier Variable", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "If multiple values exist (e.g., due to a \"Check all that apply\" instruction on a CRF), then the value for the qualifier variable should be \"MULTIPLE\" and SUPP-- should be used to store the individual responses.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0035_a011", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 35, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§4.2.8.3 Multiple Values for a Non-result Qualifier Variable", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "It is recommended that the SUPP-- QNAM value reference the corresponding standard domain variable with an appended number or letter.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0035_a012", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 35, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§4.2.8.3 Multiple Values for a Non-result Qualifier Variable", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "In some cases, the standard variable name will be shortened to meet the 8-character variable name requirement, or it may be clearer to append a meaningful character string as shown in the second Adverse Events (AE) example below, where the first 3 characters of the drug name are appended.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0035_a013", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 35, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§4.2.8.3 Multiple Values for a Non-result Qualifier Variable", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Likewise, the QLABEL value should be similar to the standard label.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0035_a014", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 35, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§4.2.8.3 Multiple Values for a Non-result Qualifier Variable", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "The values stored in QVAL should be consistent with the controlled terminology associated with the standard variable.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0035_a015", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 35, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§4.2.8.3 Multiple Values for a Non-result Qualifier Variable", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "See Section 8.4, Relating Non-standard Variable Values to a Parent Domain, for additional guidance on maintaining appropriately unique QNAM values.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": ["§8.4"], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0035_a016", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 35, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.2.8.3 Multiple Values for a Non-result Qualifier Variable", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "The following example includes selected variables from the ae.xpt and suppae.xpt datasets for a rash with locations on the face, neck, and chest.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
