{"atom_id": "ig34_p0035_a026", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 35, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.2.8.3 Multiple Values for a Non-result Qualifier Variable", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "For example, a sponsor might conduct a study with 2 study drugs (e.g., open-label study of Abcicin + Xyzamin), and may require the investigator assess causality and describe action taken for each drug for the rash:", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch04_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
