{"atom_id": "ig34_p0045_a021", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 45, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.4.7 [Use of Relative Timing Variables]", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "AESTDTC is start date (e.g., \"2006-10-01\")", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": 1, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch05_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0045_a022", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 45, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.4.7 [Use of Relative Timing Variables]", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "AEENDTC is null", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": 2, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch05_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0045_a023", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 45, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.4.7 [Use of Relative Timing Variables]", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "AEENRTPT = \"UNKNOWN\"", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": 3, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch05_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0045_a024", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 45, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.4.7 [Use of Relative Timing Variables]", "atom_type": "CODE_LITERAL", "verbatim": "UNKNOWN", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch05_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0045_a025", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 45, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.4.7 [Use of Relative Timing Variables]", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "AEENTPT is final subject contact date (e.g., \"2006-11-02\")", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": 4, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch05_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0045_a026", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 45, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.4.8 [Date and Time Reported in a Domain Based on Findings]", "atom_type": "HEADING", "verbatim": "4.4.8 Date and Time Reported in a Domain Based on Findings", "heading_level": 3, "sibling_index": 8, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch05_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0045_a027", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 45, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.4.8 [Date and Time Reported in a Domain Based on Findings]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "When the date/time of collection is reported in any domain, the date/time should go into the --DTC field (e.g., EGDTC for Date/Time of ECG).", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch05_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0045_a028", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 45, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.4.8 [Date and Time Reported in a Domain Based on Findings]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "For any domain based on the Findings general observation class (e.g., lab tests based on a specimen), the collection date is likely to be tied to when the source of the finding was captured, not necessarily when the data were recorded.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch05_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0045_a029", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 45, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.4.8 [Date and Time Reported in a Domain Based on Findings]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "In order to ensure that the critical timing information is always represented in the same variable, the --DTC variable is used to represent the time of specimen collection.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch05_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0045_a030", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 45, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.4.8 [Date and Time Reported in a Domain Based on Findings]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "For example, in the Laboratory Test Results (LB) domain, the LBDTC variable would be used for all single-point blood collections or spot urine collections.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch05_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0045_a031", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 45, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.4.8 [Date and Time Reported in a Domain Based on Findings]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "For timed lab collections (e.g., 24-hour urine collections) the LBDTC variable would be used for the start date/time of the collection and LBENDTC for the end date/time of the collection.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch05_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0045_a032", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 45, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.4.8 [Date and Time Reported in a Domain Based on Findings]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "This approach allows the single-point and interval collections to use the same date/time variables consistently across all datasets for the Findings general observation class.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch05_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0045_a033", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 45, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.4.8 [Date and Time Reported in a Domain Based on Findings]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "The following table illustrates the proper use of these variables.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch05_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0045_a034", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 45, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.4.8 [Date and Time Reported in a Domain Based on Findings]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Note that --STDTC should not be used in the Findings general observation class and is therefore blank in this table.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch05_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0045_a035", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 45, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "§4.4.8 [Date and Time Reported in a Domain Based on Findings]", "atom_type": "TABLE_HEADER", "verbatim": "Collection Type | --DTC | --STDTC | --ENDTC", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch05_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0045_a036", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 45, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "§4.4.8 [Date and Time Reported in a Domain Based on Findings]", "atom_type": "TABLE_ROW", "verbatim": "Single-point Collection | X |  | ", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": 1, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch05_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
