{"atom_id": "ig34_p0046_a022", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 46, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.4.10 [Representing Time Points]", "atom_type": "NOTE", "verbatim": "Note that VSELTM is the planned elapsed time, not the actual elapsed time. The actual elapsed time could be derived in an analysis dataset, if desired, as VSDTC-VSRFTDTC.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch05_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0046_a023", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 46, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.4.10 [Representing Time Points]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Values for these variables for urine collections taken pre-dose, and from 0-12 hours and 12-24 hours after dosing would look like the following.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch05_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0046_a024", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 46, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.4.10 [Representing Time Points]", "atom_type": "TABLE_HEADER", "verbatim": "LBTPTNUM | LBTPT | LBELTM | LBTPTREF | LBRFTDTC | LBDTC", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch05_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
