{"atom_id": "ig34_p0046_a029", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 46, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.4.10 [Representing Time Points]", "atom_type": "TABLE_ROW", "verbatim": "3 | 12-24 HOURS | PT24H | DOSE ADMINISTRATION | 2006-08-01T08:00 | 2006-08-02T08:40", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": 3, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch05_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0046_a030", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 46, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.4.10 [Representing Time Points]", "atom_type": "CODE_LITERAL", "verbatim": "PT24H", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch05_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0046_a031", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 46, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "§4.4.10 [Representing Time Points]", "atom_type": "NOTE", "verbatim": "Note that the value in LBELTM represents the end of the specimen collection interval.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch05_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0046_a032", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 46, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "§4.4.10 [Representing Time Points]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "When time points are represented in SDTMIG domains, both --TPT and --TPTNUM must be used.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch05_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0046_a033", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 46, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "§4.4.10 [Representing Time Points]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Time points may or may not have an associated --TPTREF.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch05_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0046_a034", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 46, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "§4.4.10 [Representing Time Points]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Sometimes, --TPTNUM may be used as a key for multiple values collected for the same test within a visit; as such, there is no dependence upon an anchor such as --TPTREF, but there will be a dependency upon VISITNUM.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch05_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0046_a035", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 46, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "§4.4.10 [Representing Time Points]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "In such cases, VISITNUM will be required to confer uniqueness to values of --TPTNUM.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch05_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0047_a001", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 47, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§4.4.10 [Representing Time Points]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "If the protocol describes the scheduling of a dose using a reference intervention or assessment, then --TPTREF should be populated, even if it does not contribute to uniqueness.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch05_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0047_a002", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 47, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§4.4.10 [Representing Time Points]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "The fact that time points are related to a reference time point, and what that reference time point is, are important for interpreting the data collected at the time point.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch05_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0047_a003", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 47, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§4.4.10 [Representing Time Points]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Not all time points will require all 3 variables to provide uniqueness.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch05_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0047_a004", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 47, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§4.4.10 [Representing Time Points]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "In fact, in some cases a time point may be uniquely identified without the use of VISIT, or without the use of --TPTREF, or without the use of either.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch05_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0047_a005", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 47, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§4.4.10 [Representing Time Points]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "For instance:", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch05_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0047_a006", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 47, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§4.4.10 [Representing Time Points]", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "A trial might have time points only within 1 visit, so that the contribution of VISITNUM to uniqueness is trivial. (VISITNUM would be populated, but would not contribute to uniqueness.)", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": 1, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch05_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0047_a007", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 47, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§4.4.10 [Representing Time Points]", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "A trial might have time points that do not relate to any visit, such as time points relative to a dose of drug self-administered by the subject at home. (Visit variables would not be included, but --TPTREF and other time point variables would be populated.)", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": 2, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch05_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0047_a008", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 47, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§4.4.10 [Representing Time Points]", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "A trial may have only 1 reference time point per visit, and all reference time points may be similar, so that only 1 value of --TPTREF (e.g., \"DOSE\") is needed. (--TPTREF would be populated, but would not contribute to uniqueness.)", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": 3, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch05_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0047_a009", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 47, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§4.4.10 [Representing Time Points]", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "A trial may have time points not related to a reference time point. For instance, --TPTNUM values could be used to distinguish first, second, and third repeats of a measurement scheduled without any relationship to dosing (--TPTREF and --ELTM would not be included.) In this case, where the protocol calls for repeated measurements but does not specify timing of the measurements, the --REPNUM variable could be used instead of time-point variables.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": 4, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch05_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0047_a010", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 47, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.4.10 [Representing Time Points]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "For trials with many time points, the requirement to provide uniqueness using only VISITNUM, --TPTREF, and --TPTNUM may lead to a scheme where multiple natural keys are combined into the values of one of these variables.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch05_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0047_a011", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 47, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.4.10 [Representing Time Points]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "For instance, in a crossover trial with multiple doses on multiple days within each period, either of the following options could be used.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch05_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0047_a012", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 47, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.4.10 [Representing Time Points]", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "VISITNUM might be used to designate period, --TPTREF might be used to designate the day and the dose, and --TPTNUM might be used to designate the timing relative to the reference time point.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": 1, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch05_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0047_a013", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 47, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.4.10 [Representing Time Points]", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "VISITNUM might be used to designate period and day within period, --TPTREF might be used to designate the dose within the day, and --TPTNUM might be used to designate the timing relative to the reference time point.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": 2, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch05_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0047_a014", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 47, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.4.10 [Representing Time Points]", "atom_type": "HEADING", "verbatim": "Option 1", "heading_level": 4, "sibling_index": 2, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch05_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0047_a015", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 47, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§4.4.10 [Representing Time Points]", "atom_type": "TABLE_HEADER", "verbatim": "VISIT | VISITNUM | --TPT | --TPTNUM | --TPTREF", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+batch05_4digit_fix", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
