{"atom_id": "ig34_p0083_a002", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 83, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§5.3 [Subject Elements (SE)]", "atom_type": "HEADING", "verbatim": "Example 2", "heading_level": 4, "sibling_index": 2, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0083_a003", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 83, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§5.3 [Subject Elements (SE)]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "The following data represent 2 subjects enrolled in a trial in which assignment to an arm occurs in 2 stages.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0083_a004", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 83, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§5.3 [Subject Elements (SE)]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "See Section 7.2.1, Trial Arms, Example Trial 3. In this trial, subjects were randomized at the beginning of the blinded treatment epoch, then assigned to treatment for the open treatment epoch according to their response to treatment in the blinded treatment epoch. See Section 5.2, Demographics, for other examples of ARM and ARMCD values for this trial.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": ["§7.2.1", "§5.2"], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0083_a005", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 83, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§5.3 [Subject Elements (SE)]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "In this trial, start of dosing was recorded as dates without times, so SESTDTC values include only dates.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0083_a006", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 83, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§5.3 [Subject Elements (SE)]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Epochs could not be assigned to observations that occurred on epoch transition dates on the basis of the SE dataset alone, so the sponsor's algorithms for dealing with this ambiguity were documented in the Define-XML document.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0083_a007", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 83, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§5.3 [Subject Elements (SE)]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Rows 1-2: Show data for a subject who completed only 2 elements of the trial.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0083_a008", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 83, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§5.3 [Subject Elements (SE)]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Rows 3-6: Show data for a subject who completed the trial, but received the wrong drug for the last 2 weeks of the double-blind treatment period. This has been represented by treating the period when the subject received the wrong drug as an unplanned element. Note that TAETORD, which represents the planned order of elements within an arm, has not been populated for this unplanned element. Even though this element was unplanned, the sponsor assigned a value of BLINDED TREATMENT to EPOCH.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
