{"atom_id": "ig34_p0086_a023", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 86, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "§5.5 [Subject Visits (SV)]", "atom_type": "TABLE_ROW", "verbatim": "SVPRESP | Pre-specified | Char | (NY) | Variable Qualifier | Used to indicate whether the visit was planned (i.e., visits specified in the TV domain). Value is \"Y\" for planned visits, null for unplanned visits. | Exp", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
