{"atom_id": "ig34_p0090_a010", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 90, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§5.5 [Subject Visits (SV)]", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "Row 10: Data for the screening visit was gathered over the course of six days. For this and subsequent visits, SVPRESP = \"Y\" indicates that a visit was planned and SVOCCUR = \"Y\" indicates that the visit occurred.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0090_a011", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 90, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§5.5 [Subject Visits (SV)]", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "Row 11: The visit called \"DAY 1\" started and ended as planned, on Day 1.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0090_a012", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 90, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§5.5 [Subject Visits (SV)]", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "Row 12: The visit scheduled for Day 8 occurred one day early, on Day 7.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0090_a013", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 90, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§5.5 [Subject Visits (SV)]", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "Row 13: The visit called \"WEEK 2\" did not occur due to clinic closure. SVOCCUR = \"N\" and SVREASOC contains the reason the visit did not occur.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0090_a014", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 90, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§5.5 [Subject Visits (SV)]", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "Row 14: Shows an unscheduled visit. SVUPDES provides the information that this visit dealt with evaluation of an adverse event. Since this visit was not planned, VISITDY was not populated, SVPRESP and SVOCCUR are both null. VISITNUM is populated as required, but the sponsor chose not to populate VISIT. Data collected at this encounter may be in a Findings domain such as EG, LB, or VS, in which VISITNUM is treated as an important timing variable. This visit was over remote audio video due to having an adverse event during a pandemic.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0090_a015", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 90, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§5.5 [Subject Visits (SV)]", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "Row 15: This subject had their last visit, a follow-up visit on study day 26, eight days after the unscheduled visit.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
