{"atom_id": "ig34_p0096_a007", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 96, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§6.1.1 [Procedure Agents (AG)]", "atom_type": "HEADING", "verbatim": "Example 2", "heading_level": 4, "sibling_index": 2, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R9", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0096_a008", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 96, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.1.1 [Procedure Agents (AG)]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "In this example, first there was a check that the subject had not taken a short-acting bronchodilator in the previous 4 hours (Concomitant/Prior Medications (CM) domain). Then the procedure agent (AG domain) was given as part of a reversibility assessment. Spirometry measurements (RE domain) were obtained before and after agent administration. An identifier was assigned to the reversibility test and this identifier was used to be link data across the multiple SDTM domains in which the data are represented.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R9", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0096_a009", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 96, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.1.1 [Procedure Agents (AG)]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "The question as to whether a short-acting bronchodilator was administered in the 4 hours prior to the reversibility assessment is represented in the CM domain because this prior administration would have been for therapeutic effect, not as part of the procedure. The question asked was about the administration of any short-acting bronchodilator, rather than a specific medication, so both CMTRT and CMCAT are populated with \"SHORT-ACTING BRONCHODILATOR\", which describes a group of medications. The CMSPID value RV1 was used to indicate that this question was associated with the reversibility test.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R9", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0096_a010", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 96, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.1.1 [Procedure Agents (AG)]", "atom_type": "CODE_LITERAL", "verbatim": "cm.xpt", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R9", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0096_a011", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 96, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.1.1 [Procedure Agents (AG)]", "atom_type": "TABLE_HEADER", "verbatim": "Row | STUDYID | DOMAIN | USUBJID | CMSEQ | CMSPID | CMTRT | CMCAT | CMPRESP | CMOCCUR | CMEVLINT", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R9", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0096_a012", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 96, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.1.1 [Procedure Agents (AG)]", "atom_type": "TABLE_ROW", "verbatim": "1 | XYZ | CM | XYZ-001-001 | 1 | RV1 | SHORT-ACTING BRONCHODILATOR | SHORT-ACTING BRONCHODILATOR | Y | N | -PT4H", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R9", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0096_a013", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 96, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.1.1 [Procedure Agents (AG)]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "The administration of albuterol as part of the reversibility procedure is represented in the AG domain. The AGSPID value RV1 was used to indicate that this administration was associated with the reversibility test.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R9", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
