{"atom_id": "ig34_p0096_a015", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 96, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.1.1 [Procedure Agents (AG)]", "atom_type": "TABLE_HEADER", "verbatim": "Row | STUDYID | DOMAIN | USUBJID | AGSEQ | AGSPID | AGTRT | AGPRESP | AGOCCUR | AGDOSE | AGDOSU | AGDOSFRM | AGDOSFRQ | AGROUTE | VISIT | AGSTDTC", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R9", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0096_a016", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 96, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.1.1 [Procedure Agents (AG)]", "atom_type": "TABLE_ROW", "verbatim": "1 | XYZ | AG | XYZ-001-001 | 1 | RV1 | ALBUTEROL | Y | Y | 2 | PUFF | AEROSOL | ONCE | RESPIRATORY (INHALATION) | VISIT 2 | 2013-06-18T10:05", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R9", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0096_a017", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 96, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "§6.1.1 [Procedure Agents (AG)]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "The sponsor populated REGRPID with RV1 to indicate that these pulmonary function tests were associated with the reversibility test. The spirometer used in the testing is identified in SPDEVID. See the SDTMIG-MD (available at https://www.cdisc.org/standards/foundational/medical-devices-sdtmig/) for information about representing device-related information.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R9", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0096_a018", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 96, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "§6.1.1 [Procedure Agents (AG)]", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "Row 1:\tShows the results for the pre-bronchodilator FEV1 test performed as part of a reversibility assessment. The timing reference variables RETPT, RETPTNUM, REELTM, RETPTREF, and RERFTDTC show that this test was performed 5 minutes before the bronchodilator challenge.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R9", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0096_a019", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 96, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "§6.1.1 [Procedure Agents (AG)]", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "Row 2:\tShows the results for FEV1 test performed 20 minutes after the bronchodilator challenge.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R9", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0096_a020", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 96, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "§6.1.1 [Procedure Agents (AG)]", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "Row 3:\tBecause the percentage reversibility was collected on the CRF, it is included in the SDTM dataset.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R9", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
