{"atom_id": "ig34_p0102_a003", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 102, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§6.1.2 [Concomitant/Prior Medications (CM)]", "atom_type": "HEADING", "verbatim": "Example 2", "heading_level": 5, "sibling_index": 2, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R10", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0102_a004", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 102, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§6.1.2 [Concomitant/Prior Medications (CM)]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "In this example study, it was of particular interest whether subjects use any anticonvulsant medications.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R10", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0102_a005", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 102, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§6.1.2 [Concomitant/Prior Medications (CM)]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "The medication history, dosing, and so on was not of interest; the study only asked for the anticonvulsants to which subjects were exposed.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R10", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
