{"atom_id": "ig34_p0102_a009", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 102, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.1.2 [Concomitant/Prior Medications (CM)]", "atom_type": "HEADING", "verbatim": "Example 3", "heading_level": 5, "sibling_index": 3, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R10", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0102_a010", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 102, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.1.2 [Concomitant/Prior Medications (CM)]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Sponsors often are interested in whether subjects are exposed to specific concomitant medications, and collect this information using a checklist.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R10", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0102_a011", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 102, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.1.2 [Concomitant/Prior Medications (CM)]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "This example is for a study that had a particular interest in the antidepressant medications that subjects used.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R10", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0102_a012", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 102, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.1.2 [Concomitant/Prior Medications (CM)]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "For the study's purposes, absence is just as important as presence of a medication.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R10", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0102_a013", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 102, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.1.2 [Concomitant/Prior Medications (CM)]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "This can be clearly shown using CMOCCUR.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R10", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0102_a014", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 102, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.1.2 [Concomitant/Prior Medications (CM)]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "In this example, CMPRESP shows that the subjects were specifically asked if they use any of 3 antidepressants (Zoloft, Prozac, and Paxil).", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R10", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0102_a015", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 102, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.1.2 [Concomitant/Prior Medications (CM)]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "The value of CMOCCUR indicates the response to the prespecified medication question.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R10", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0102_a016", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 102, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.1.2 [Concomitant/Prior Medications (CM)]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "CMSTAT indicates whether the response was missing for a prespecified medication, and CMREASND shows the reason for missing response.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R10", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0102_a017", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 102, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.1.2 [Concomitant/Prior Medications (CM)]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "The medication details (e.g., dose, frequency) were not of interest in this study.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R10", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0102_a018", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 102, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.1.2 [Concomitant/Prior Medications (CM)]", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "Row 1: Medication use was solicited and the medication was taken.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": 1, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R10", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
