{"atom_id": "ig34_p0102_a023", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 102, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.1.2 [Concomitant/Prior Medications (CM)]", "atom_type": "TABLE_ROW", "verbatim": "2 | ABC123 | CM | 1 | 2 | PROZAC | Y | N | | |", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R10", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z", "note": "F-B11-RA-1 inline fix: trailing CMREASND empty pipe added per R8"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0102_a024", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 102, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.1.2 [Concomitant/Prior Medications (CM)]", "atom_type": "TABLE_ROW", "verbatim": "3 | ABC123 | CM | 1 | 3 | PAXIL | Y | | NOT DONE | Didn't ask due to interruption", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R10", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0102_a025", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 102, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "§6.1.2 [Concomitant/Prior Medications (CM)]", "atom_type": "HEADING", "verbatim": "Example 4", "heading_level": 5, "sibling_index": 4, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R10", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0102_a026", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 102, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "§6.1.2 [Concomitant/Prior Medications (CM)]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "In this hepatitis C study, collection of data on prior treatments included reason for discontinuation.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R10", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0102_a027", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 102, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "§6.1.2 [Concomitant/Prior Medications (CM)]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Because hepatitis C is usually treated with a combinations of medications, CMGRPID was used to group records into regimens.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R10", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0102_a028", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 102, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "§6.1.2 [Concomitant/Prior Medications (CM)]", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "Rows 1-3: This subject's treatment consisted of the 3 medications grouped by means of CMGRPID = \"1\". The subject completed the scheduled treatment.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": 1, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R10", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0102_a029", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 102, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "§6.1.2 [Concomitant/Prior Medications (CM)]", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "Rows 4-6: Another subject received the same set of 3 medications. For this subject, as also shown using CMGRPID = \"1\", Note, however, that the fact that the same CMGRPID value has been used for the same set of medications for subjects \"ABC123-765\" and \"ABC123-899\" is coincidence; CMGRPID groups records only within a subject. This subject stopped the regimen due to side effects.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": 2, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R10", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
