{"atom_id": "ig34_p0103_a006", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 103, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§6.1.2 [Concomitant/Prior Medications (CM)]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "In this rheumatoid arthritis (RA) study, the sponsor collected medications using the category \"Prior RA Medications\", then collected information on whether the subject had received certain medication classes, represented as subcategories. If a subject did receive medications in a subcategory, information about those medications was collected. This example shows data for 2 subjects who received prior RA medications. It includes data only about their prior disease-modifying antirheumatic drugs (DMARDs); information about other kinds of prior RA medications is not included.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R10+option_E_rerun_p103", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0103_a007", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 103, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.1.2 [Concomitant/Prior Medications (CM)]", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "Row 1: Shows that subject 101 received prior RA medications. The values of CMTRT and CMCAT are the same, indicating that this record represents the response to a question about a category of medications, rather than an individual medication.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R10+option_E_rerun_p103", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0103_a008", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 103, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.1.2 [Concomitant/Prior Medications (CM)]", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "Row 2: Shows that subject 101 did not receive prior DMARDs. The values in CMTRT and CMSCAT are the same, indicating that this record represents the response to a question about a group of medications, rather than an individual medication.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R10+option_E_rerun_p103", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0103_a009", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 103, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.1.2 [Concomitant/Prior Medications (CM)]", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "Row 3: Shows that subject 102 received prior RA medications.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R10+option_E_rerun_p103", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
