{"atom_id": "ig34_p0111_a003", "source": "SDTMIG v3.4 (no header footer).pdf", "source_short": "ig34", "page": 111, "atom_index_on_page": 3, "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "This is an example of a double-blind study comparing drug X extended release (ER; 2 500-mg tablets once daily) vs. drug Z (2 250-mg tablets once daily). Per example CRFs, subject ABC1001 took 2 tablets from 2011-01-14 to 2011-01-28 and subject ABC2001 took 2 tablets within the same timeframe but missed dosing on 2011-01-24.", "parent_section": "§6.1.3.3 [Exposure/Exposure as Collected Examples]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "cross_refs": null, "figure_ref": null, "table_ref": null, "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R14"}
