{"atom_id": "ig34_p0114_a001", "source": "SDTMIG v3.4 (no header footer).pdf", "source_short": "ig34", "page": 114, "atom_index_on_page": 1, "atom_type": "HEADING", "verbatim": "Example 4", "parent_section": "§6.1.3.3 [Exposure/Exposure as Collected Examples]", "heading_level": 5, "sibling_index": 4, "cross_refs": null, "figure_ref": null, "table_ref": null, "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R14"}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0114_a002", "source": "SDTMIG v3.4 (no header footer).pdf", "source_short": "ig34", "page": 114, "atom_index_on_page": 2, "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "The study in this example was an open-label study examining the tolerability of different doses of drug A. The study drug was taken orally, daily for 3 months. Dose adjustments were allowed as needed in response to tolerability or efficacy issues.", "parent_section": "§6.1.3.3 [Exposure/Exposure as Collected Examples]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "cross_refs": null, "figure_ref": null, "table_ref": null, "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R14"}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0114_a003", "source": "SDTMIG v3.4 (no header footer).pdf", "source_short": "ig34", "page": 114, "atom_index_on_page": 3, "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "The EX dataset shows administrations collected in the protocol-specified unit, mg. No EC dataset was needed because the open-label administrations were collected in the protocol-specified unit; EC would be an exact duplicate of the entire EX domain.", "parent_section": "§6.1.3.3 [Exposure/Exposure as Collected Examples]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "cross_refs": null, "figure_ref": null, "table_ref": null, "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R14"}
