{"atom_id": "ig34_p0114_a026", "source": "SDTMIG v3.4 (no header footer).pdf", "source_short": "ig34", "page": 114, "atom_index_on_page": 26, "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "The EC dataset shows the administrations as collected. The time-point variables ECTPT and ECTPTNUM were used to describe the time of day of administration. This use of time-point variables is novel, representing data about multiple time points, 1 on each day of administration, rather than data for a single time point.", "parent_section": "§6.1.3.3 [Exposure/Exposure as Collected Examples]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "cross_refs": null, "figure_ref": null, "table_ref": null, "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+TOC_anchor+R1-R14"}
