{"atom_id": "ig34_p0132_a011", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 132, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§6.1.6 [Substance Use (SU)]", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "How many cups today", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+R10..R15", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0132_a012", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 132, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.1.6 [Substance Use (SU)]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "SUCAT allows the records to be grouped into smoking-related data and caffeine-related data. In this example, the treatments are prespecified on the CRF page, so SUTRT does not require a standardized SUDECOD equivalent.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+R10..R15", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0132_a013", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 132, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.1.6 [Substance Use (SU)]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Not shown: A subject who never smoked does not have a tobacco record. Alternatively, a row for the subject could have been included with SUOCCUR = \"N\" and null dosing and timing fields; the interpretation would be the same. A subject who did not drink any caffeinated drinks on the day of the assessment does not have any caffeine records. A subject who never smoked and did not drink caffeinated drinks on the day of the assessment does not appear in the dataset.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+R10..R15", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0132_a014", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 132, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.1.6 [Substance Use (SU)]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Row 1: Subject 1234005 is a 2-pack/day current smoker. \"Current\" implies that smoking started sometime before the time the question was asked (SUSTTPT = \"2006-01-01\", SUSTRTPT = \"BEFORE\") and had not ended as of that date (SUENTTP = \"2006-01-01\", SUENRTPT = \"ONGOING\"). See Section 4.4.7, Use of Relative Timing Variables for the use of these variables. Both the beginning and ending reference time points for this question are the date of the assessment.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": ["§4.4.7"], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+R10..R15", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0132_a015", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 132, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.1.6 [Substance Use (SU)]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Row 2: Subject 1234005 drank 3 cups of coffee on the day of the assessment.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+R10..R15", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0132_a016", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 132, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.1.6 [Substance Use (SU)]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Row 3: Subject 1234006 is a former smoker. The date this subject began smoking is unknown, but it was sometime before the assessment date; this is shown by the values of SUSTTPT and SUSTRTPT. The end date of smoking was collected, so SUENTPT and SUENRTPT are not populated. Instead, the end date is in SUENDTC.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+R10..R15", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0132_a017", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 132, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.1.6 [Substance Use (SU)]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Row 4: Subject 1234006 drank tea on the day of the assessment.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+R10..R15", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0132_a018", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 132, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.1.6 [Substance Use (SU)]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Row 5: Subject 1234006 drank coffee on the day of the assessment.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+R10..R15", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0132_a019", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 132, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "§6.1.6 [Substance Use (SU)]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Row 6: Subject 1234007 had missing data for the smoking questions; this is indicated by SUSTAT = \"NOT DONE\". The reason is in SUREASND.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+R10..R15", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
