{"atom_id": "ig34_p0136_a002", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 136, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§6.2.1 [Adverse Events (AE)]", "atom_type": "TABLE_ROW", "verbatim": "| AESHOSP | Requires or Prolongs Hospitalization | Char | (NY) | Record Qualifier | Did the serious event require or prolong hospitalization? Valid values are \"Y\" and \"N\". | Perm |", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+R10..R15+OptionE", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
