{"atom_id": "ig34_p0149_a005", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 149, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§6.2.3 [Clinical Events (CE)]", "atom_type": "TABLE_ROW", "verbatim": "| CEREASND | Reason Clinical Event Not Collected | Char | | Record Qualifier | Describes the reason clinical event data was not collected. Used in conjunction with CESTAT when value is \"NOT DONE\". | Perm |", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+R15", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
