{"atom_id": "ig34_p0151_a0028", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 151, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "§6.2.3 [Clinical Events]", "atom_type": "HEADING", "verbatim": "Example 2", "heading_level": 5, "sibling_index": 2, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-5", "ts": "2026-04-25T19:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0151_a0029", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 151, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "§6.2.3 [Clinical Events]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "In this example, the CRF included both questions about prespecified clinical events (events not reportable as AEs in the context of this study) and places for specifying additional clinical events.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-5", "ts": "2026-04-25T19:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0151_a0030", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 151, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "§6.2.3 [Clinical Events]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "No explicit evaluation interval is given, but the implicit time frame for the question is \"during the study.\"", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-5", "ts": "2026-04-25T19:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0151_a0031", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 151, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "§6.2.3 [Clinical Events]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Although this example CRF shows only 1 row for each symptom, if a symptom occurred more than once, data would be collected for each time it occurred.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-5", "ts": "2026-04-25T19:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0151_a0032", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 151, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "§6.2.3 [Clinical Events]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "These data are about the event as a whole, so they are represented in the CE domain.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-5", "ts": "2026-04-25T19:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0152_a0001", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 152, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§6.2.3 [Clinical Events]", "atom_type": "NOTE", "verbatim": "In this example, the use of \"Other, Specify\" for clinical events is likely to require manual review of the data, to be sure that none of the write-in terms should have been reported as adverse events based on the sponsor's criteria for this study.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-5", "ts": "2026-04-25T19:00:00Z"}}
