{"atom_id": "ig34_p0152_a0016", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 152, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.2.3 [Clinical Events]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Rows 1-2:\tShow records for 2 instances of the prespecified clinical event, nausea. The CEPRESP value of \"Y\" indicates that there was a probing question; the response to the probe (CEOCCUR) was \"Yes\". CEPRESP and CEOCCUR are included in both records for \"Nausea\". The record includes additional data about the event.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-5", "ts": "2026-04-25T19:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0152_a0017", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 152, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.2.3 [Clinical Events]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Row 3:\tShows a record for the prespecified clinical event, vomit. The CEPRESP value of \"Y\" indicates that there was a probing question; the response to the question (CEOCCUR) was \"No\". Because there was no event, severity and start and end dates are null.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-5", "ts": "2026-04-25T19:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0152_a0018", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 152, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.2.3 [Clinical Events]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Row 4:\tShows a record for the prespecified clinical event, diarrhea. The value \"Y\" for CEPRESP indicates it was prespecified. The CESTAT value of NOT DONE indicates that the probing question was not asked or that there was no answer.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-5", "ts": "2026-04-25T19:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0152_a0019", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 152, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.2.3 [Clinical Events]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Row 5:\tShows a record for a write-in clinical event recorded in the \"Other, Specify\" space. Because this event was not prespecified, CEPRESP and CEOCCUR are null. See Section 4.2.7.3, \"Specify\" Values for Topic Variables,for further information on populating the topic variable when \"Other, Specify\" is used on the CRF.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": ["§4.2.7.3"], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-5", "ts": "2026-04-25T19:00:00Z"}}
