{"atom_id": "ig34_p0153_a0026", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 153, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.2.3 [Clinical Events]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "The collected data do not meet criteria for representation in FA. Data about the most recent pre-study fracture were represented in the Medical History (MH) domain, and data about fractures during the study were represented in the CE domain.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-5", "ts": "2026-04-25T19:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0153_a0027", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 153, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.2.3 [Clinical Events]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "The supplemental qualifier MHCAUSE or CECAUSE (depending on domain) was used to represent the response to the question, \"How did the fracture occur?\"", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-5", "ts": "2026-04-25T19:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0153_a0028", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 153, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.2.3 [Clinical Events]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "The supplemental qualifier MHCPLIND or CECPLIND (depending on domain) was used to represent the response to the question, \"Were there any complications of the fracture?\"", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-5", "ts": "2026-04-25T19:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0153_a0029", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 153, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.2.3 [Clinical Events]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "The codelist used for AECONTRT (NY) was used for MHCONTRT and CECONTRT.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-5", "ts": "2026-04-25T19:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0153_a0030", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 153, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.2.3 [Clinical Events]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Row 1:\tThe subject had only 1 fracture in the last 5 years. This fracture required treatment (MHCONTRT = \"Y\").", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-5", "ts": "2026-04-25T19:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0153_a0031", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 153, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.2.3 [Clinical Events]", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Row 2:\tThis subject had a complication (see supplemental qualifier MHCPLIND in suppmh.xpt dataset), which was represented as a separate medical history event. MHGRPID was used to group this with the fracture for which it was a complication. No separate start date for this complication was collected, so MHSTDTC is blank.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-5", "ts": "2026-04-25T19:00:00Z"}}
