{"atom_id": "ig34_p0160_a0006", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 160, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§6.2.4 Disposition (DS)", "atom_type": "HEADING", "verbatim": "Example 3", "heading_level": 5, "sibling_index": 3, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-5", "ts": "2026-04-25T19:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0160_a0007", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 160, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§6.2.4 Disposition (DS)", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "In this study, disposition of study participation was collected for the treatment and follow-up epochs.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-5", "ts": "2026-04-25T19:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0160_a0008", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 160, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§6.2.4 Disposition (DS)", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "For these records, the value in EPOCH was taken from the CRF.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-5", "ts": "2026-04-25T19:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0160_a0009", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 160, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§6.2.4 Disposition (DS)", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Data on screen failures were not submitted for this study, so all submitted subjects completed screening; the sponsor chose not to collect data on disposition of the screening epoch.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-5", "ts": "2026-04-25T19:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0160_a0010", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 160, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§6.2.4 Disposition (DS)", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Data on protocol milestones were not collected, but data were collected if a subject's treatment was unblinded.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-5", "ts": "2026-04-25T19:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0160_a0011", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 160, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§6.2.4 Disposition (DS)", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "For these records, EPOCH represents the epoch during which the blind was broken.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-5", "ts": "2026-04-25T19:00:00Z"}}
