{"atom_id": "ig34_p0176_a0015", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 176, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.2.6 Medical History (MH)", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "This is an example of a medical history CRF where the history of specific (prespecified) conditions is solicited. The conditions were not coded using a standard dictionary. The data were collected as part of the screening visit.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-7_batch18", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0176_a0016", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 176, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.2.6 Medical History (MH)", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "Rows 1-9:\tMHPRESP = \"Y\" indicates that these conditions were specifically queried. Presence or absence of the condition is represented in MHOCCUR.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-7_batch18", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0176_a0017", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 176, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.2.6 Medical History (MH)", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "Row 10:\tThere was also a specific question about asthma, as indicated by MHPRESP = \"Y\", but this question was not asked. Because the question was not asked, MHOCCUR is null and MHSTAT = \"NOT DONE\". In this case, a reason for the absence of a response was collected, and this is represented in MHREASND.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-7_batch18", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
