{"atom_id": "ig34_p0177_a0020", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 177, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "§6.2.6 Medical History (MH)", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "This example shows data from a study in which data were collected about whether subjects had had any respiratory infections in the prior 6 months and, if they had, collected data on those respiratory infections. The example shows data for 2 subjects.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-7_batch18", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0177_a0021", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 177, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "§6.2.6 Medical History (MH)", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "Row 1:\tShows that subject 203 had no respiratory infections during the evaluation interval (the prior 6 months). The same value (\"Respiratory Infections\") in both MHTERM and MHCAT indicates that the occurrence question was about a group of medical conditions rather than a specific single medical condition.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-7_batch18", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0177_a0022", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 177, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "§6.2.6 Medical History (MH)", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "Row 2:\tShows that subject 204 did have at least 1 respiratory infection during the evaluation interval.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-7_batch18", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0178_a0001", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 178, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§6.2.6 Medical History (MH)", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "Row 3:\tShows that subject 204 had a common cold during the evaluation interval. They did not provide an end date, but indicated that the infection had ended.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-7_batch18", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0178_a0002", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 178, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§6.2.6 Medical History (MH)", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "Row 4:\tShows that subject 204 had bronchitis during the evaluation interval, and that an end date for the infection was provided.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-7_batch18", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
