{"atom_id": "ig34_p0178_a0020", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 178, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.2.7 Protocol Deviations (DV)", "atom_type": "TABLE_ROW", "verbatim": "| DVSPID | Sponsor-Defined Identifier | Char | | Identifier | Sponsor-defined reference number. May be preprinted on the CRF as an explicit line identifier or defined in the sponsor's operational database. Example: Line number on a CRF page. | Perm |", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-7_batch18", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0178_a0021", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 178, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.2.7 Protocol Deviations (DV)", "atom_type": "TABLE_ROW", "verbatim": "| DVTERM | Protocol Deviation Term | Char | | Topic | Verbatim name of the protocol deviation criterion. Example: \"IVRS PROCESS DEVIATION - NO DOSE CALL PERFORMED\". DVTERM values will map to the controlled terminology in DVDECOD (e.g., \"TREATMENT DEVIATION\"). | Req |", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-7_batch18", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0178_a0022", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 178, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.2.7 Protocol Deviations (DV)", "atom_type": "TABLE_ROW", "verbatim": "| DVDECOD | Protocol Deviation Coded Term | Char | * | Synonym Qualifier | Controlled terminology for the name of the protocol deviation. Examples: \"SUBJECT NOT WITHDRAWN AS PER PROTOCOL\", \"SELECTION CRITERIA NOT MET\", \"EXCLUDED CONCOMITANT MEDICATION\", \"TREATMENT DEVIATION\". | Perm |", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-7_batch18", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
