{"atom_id": "ig34_p0180_a0014", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 180, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.3.1 Product Accountability (DA)", "atom_type": "TABLE_ROW", "verbatim": "| DAREFID | Reference ID | Char | | Identifier | Optional internal or external identifier such as a code from the product packaging (e.g., bottle label, package label, kit label). | Perm |", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-7_batch18", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0180_a0015", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 180, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.3.1 Product Accountability (DA)", "atom_type": "TABLE_ROW", "verbatim": "| DASPID | Sponsor-Defined Identifier | Char | | Identifier | Sponsor-defined reference number. May be preprinted on the CRF as an explicit line identifier or defined in the sponsor's operational database. Examples: Line number on the Product Accountability CRF page, a code from the product packaging (e.g., bottle label, package label, kit label). | Perm |", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-7_batch18", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0180_a0016", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 180, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.3.1 Product Accountability (DA)", "atom_type": "TABLE_ROW", "verbatim": "| DALNKID | Link ID | Char | | Identifier | Identifier used to link related records across domains. This may be a one-to-one or a one-to-many relationship. | Perm |", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-7_batch18", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0180_a0017", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 180, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.3.1 Product Accountability (DA)", "atom_type": "TABLE_ROW", "verbatim": "| DALNKGRP | Link Group ID | Char | | Identifier | Identifier used to link related records across domains. This will usually be a many-to-one relationship. | Perm |", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-7_batch18", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0180_a0018", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 180, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.3.1 Product Accountability (DA)", "atom_type": "TABLE_ROW", "verbatim": "| DATESTCD | Short Name of Accountability Assessment | Char | (DATESTCD) | Topic | Short character value for DATEST used as a column name when converting a dataset from a vertical format to a horizontal format. The short value can be up to 8 characters and cannot begin with a number or contain characters other than letters, numbers, or underscores. Examples: \"DISPAMT\", \"RETAMT\". | Req |", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-7_batch18", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0180_a0019", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 180, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.3.1 Product Accountability (DA)", "atom_type": "TABLE_ROW", "verbatim": "| DATEST | Name of Accountability Assessment | Char | (DATEST) | Synonym Qualifier | Verbatim name corresponding to the topic variable of the test or examination used to obtain the product accountability assessment. The value in DATEST cannot be longer than 40 characters. Examples: \"Dispensed Amount\", \"Returned Amount\". | Req |", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-7_batch18", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0180_a0020", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 180, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "§6.3.1 Product Accountability (DA)", "atom_type": "TABLE_ROW", "verbatim": "| DACAT | Category | Char | * | Grouping Qualifier | Used to define a category of topic-variable values. Examples: \"STUDY MEDICATION\", \"RESCUE MEDICATION\". | Perm |", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-7_batch18", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0180_a0021", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 180, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "§6.3.1 Product Accountability (DA)", "atom_type": "TABLE_ROW", "verbatim": "| DASCAT | Subcategory | Char | * | Grouping Qualifier | Used to define a further categorization level for a group of related records. | Perm |", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-7_batch18", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0180_a0022", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 180, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "§6.3.1 Product Accountability (DA)", "atom_type": "TABLE_ROW", "verbatim": "| DAORRES | Result or Finding in Original Units | Char | | Result Qualifier | Result of the product accountability assessment as originally received or collected. | Exp |", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-7_batch18", "ts": "2026-04-25T00:00:00Z"}}
