{"atom_id":"ig34_p0181_a001","source":"SDTMIG_v3.4","page":181,"page_region":"top","parent_section":"§6.3.1 Product Accountability (DA)","atom_type":"TABLE_ROW","verbatim":"| DASTRESC | Result or Finding in Standard Format | Char | | Result Qualifier | Contains the result value for all product accountability assessments copied or derived from DAORRES, in a standard format or in standard units. DASTRESC should store all results or findings in character format; if results are numeric, they should also be stored in numeric format in DASTRESN. | Exp |","heading_level":null,"sibling_index":null,"figure_ref":null,"cross_refs":[],"extracted_by":{"subagent_type":"oh-my-claudecode:executor","prompt_version":"P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-7","ts":"2026-04-26T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id":"ig34_p0181_a002","source":"SDTMIG_v3.4","page":181,"page_region":"top","parent_section":"§6.3.1 Product Accountability (DA)","atom_type":"TABLE_ROW","verbatim":"| DASTRESN | Numeric Result/Finding in Standard Units | Num | | Result Qualifier | Used for continuous or numeric results or findings in standard format; copied in numeric format from DASTRESC. DASTRESN should store all numeric test results or findings. | Perm |","heading_level":null,"sibling_index":null,"figure_ref":null,"cross_refs":[],"extracted_by":{"subagent_type":"oh-my-claudecode:executor","prompt_version":"P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-7","ts":"2026-04-26T00:00:00Z"}}
