{"atom_id":"ig34_p0183_a012","source":"SDTMIG_v3.4","page":183,"page_region":"middle","parent_section":"§6.3.2 Death Details (DD)","atom_type":"TABLE_ROW","verbatim":"| DDTESTCD | Death Detail Assessment Short Name | Char | (DTHDXCD) | Topic | Short name of the measurement, test, or examination described in DDTEST. It can be used as a column name when converting a dataset from a vertical to a horizontal format. The value in DDTESTCD cannot be longer than 8 characters, nor can it start with a number (e.g., \"1TEST\" is not valid). DDTESTCD cannot contain characters other than letters, numbers, or underscores. Examples: \"PRCDTH\", \"SECDTH\". | Req |","heading_level":null,"sibling_index":null,"figure_ref":null,"cross_refs":["(DTHDXCD)"],"extracted_by":{"subagent_type":"oh-my-claudecode:executor","prompt_version":"P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-7","ts":"2026-04-26T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id":"ig34_p0183_a013","source":"SDTMIG_v3.4","page":183,"page_region":"middle","parent_section":"§6.3.2 Death Details (DD)","atom_type":"TABLE_ROW","verbatim":"| DDTEST | Death Detail Assessment Name | Char | (DTHDX) | Synonym Qualifier | Long name for DDTESTCD. The value in DDTEST cannot be longer than 40 characters. Examples: \"Primary Cause of Death\", \"Secondary Cause of Death\". | Req |","heading_level":null,"sibling_index":null,"figure_ref":null,"cross_refs":["(DTHDX)"],"extracted_by":{"subagent_type":"oh-my-claudecode:executor","prompt_version":"P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-7","ts":"2026-04-26T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id":"ig34_p0183_a014","source":"SDTMIG_v3.4","page":183,"page_region":"middle","parent_section":"§6.3.2 Death Details (DD)","atom_type":"TABLE_ROW","verbatim":"| DDORRES | Result or Finding as Collected | Char | | Result Qualifier | Result of the test defined in DDTEST, as originally received or collected. | Exp |","heading_level":null,"sibling_index":null,"figure_ref":null,"cross_refs":[],"extracted_by":{"subagent_type":"oh-my-claudecode:executor","prompt_version":"P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-7","ts":"2026-04-26T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id":"ig34_p0183_a015","source":"SDTMIG_v3.4","page":183,"page_region":"middle","parent_section":"§6.3.2 Death Details (DD)","atom_type":"TABLE_ROW","verbatim":"| DDSTRESC | Character Result/Finding in Std Format | Char | | Result Qualifier | Contains the result or finding copied or derived from DDORRES in a standard format. | Exp |","heading_level":null,"sibling_index":null,"figure_ref":null,"cross_refs":[],"extracted_by":{"subagent_type":"oh-my-claudecode:executor","prompt_version":"P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-7","ts":"2026-04-26T00:00:00Z"}}
