{"atom_id":"ig34_p0191_a028","source":"SDTMIG_v3.4","page":191,"page_region":"middle","parent_section":"§6.3.3 ECG Test Results (EG)","atom_type":"LIST_ITEM","verbatim":"Rows 1-2: Show the first beat recorded. The first beat was considered to be the beat for which the recording contained a complete P-wave. It was assigned EGBEATNO = \"1\". There is no RR measurement for this beat because RR is measured as the duration (time) between the peak of the R-wave in the reported single beat and peak of the R-wave in the preceding single beat, and the partial recording that preceded EGBEATNO = \"1\" did not contain an R-wave. EGDTC was the date/time of the individual beat.","heading_level":null,"sibling_index":null,"figure_ref":null,"cross_refs":["EGBEATNO","EGDTC"],"extracted_by":{"subagent_type":"oh-my-claudecode:executor","prompt_version":"P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-7","ts":"2026-04-26T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id":"ig34_p0191_a029","source":"SDTMIG_v3.4","page":191,"page_region":"bottom","parent_section":"§6.3.3 ECG Test Results (EG)","atom_type":"LIST_ITEM","verbatim":"Rows 3-5: EGBEATNO = \"2\" had an RR measurement, since the R-wave of the preceding beat (EGBEATNO = \"1\") was recorded.","heading_level":null,"sibling_index":null,"figure_ref":null,"cross_refs":["EGBEATNO"],"extracted_by":{"subagent_type":"oh-my-claudecode:executor","prompt_version":"P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-7","ts":"2026-04-26T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id":"ig34_p0191_a030","source":"SDTMIG_v3.4","page":191,"page_region":"bottom","parent_section":"§6.3.3 ECG Test Results (EG)","atom_type":"LIST_ITEM","verbatim":"Rows 6-8: There is a 1-hour gap between beats 2 and 3 due to electrical interference or other artifacts that prevented measurements from being recorded. Note that EGBEATNO = \"3\" does have an RR measurement because the partial beat preceding EGBEATNO = \"3\" contained an R-wave.","heading_level":null,"sibling_index":null,"figure_ref":null,"cross_refs":["EGBEATNO"],"extracted_by":{"subagent_type":"oh-my-claudecode:executor","prompt_version":"P0_writer_pdf_v1.2_inline_R10-15_O26_NEW1-7","ts":"2026-04-26T00:00:00Z"}}
