{"atom_id": "ig34_p0225_a005", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 225, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.3.5.4 Genomics Findings (GF)", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Identifying information for the gene panel used to generate the result is in the DI domain. The gene panel is represented in SDTM, as the panel used as part of the wet laboratory methodology may change and affects interpretation of the result. The platform in which the gene panel was used is not represented, because it does not provide additional context for the result.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2+inline-R10-R15+O-P1-26+NEW1-NEW8", "ts": "2026-04-26T00:00:00Z"}}
