{"atom_id":"ig34_p0242_a019","source":"SDTMIG_v3.4","page":242,"page_region":"middle","parent_section":"§6.3.5.6 Laboratory Test Results (LB)","atom_type":"TABLE_ROW","verbatim":"| LBORRESU | Original Units | Char | (UNIT) | Variable Qualifier | Original units in which the data were collected. The unit for LBORRES. Example: \"g/L\". | Exp |","heading_level":null,"sibling_index":null,"figure_ref":null,"cross_refs":[],"extracted_by":{"subagent_type":"oh-my-claudecode:executor","prompt_version":"P0_writer_pdf_v1.2","ts":"2026-04-26T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id":"ig34_p0242_a020","source":"SDTMIG_v3.4","page":242,"page_region":"middle","parent_section":"§6.3.5.6 Laboratory Test Results (LB)","atom_type":"TABLE_ROW","verbatim":"| LBRESSCL | Result Scale | Char | (RSLSCLRS) | Record Qualifier | Classifies the scale of the original result value; for example, whether the result is ordinal, nominal, quantitative, or narrative. | Perm |","heading_level":null,"sibling_index":null,"figure_ref":null,"cross_refs":[],"extracted_by":{"subagent_type":"oh-my-claudecode:executor","prompt_version":"P0_writer_pdf_v1.2","ts":"2026-04-26T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id":"ig34_p0242_a021","source":"SDTMIG_v3.4","page":242,"page_region":"bottom","parent_section":"§6.3.5.6 Laboratory Test Results (LB)","atom_type":"TABLE_ROW","verbatim":"| LBRESTYP | Result Type | Char | (RESTYPRS) | Record Qualifier | Classifies the kind of result (i.e., property type) originally reported for the test. Examples include substance concentration, proportion, mass rate, and arbitrary concentration. | Perm |","heading_level":null,"sibling_index":null,"figure_ref":null,"cross_refs":[],"extracted_by":{"subagent_type":"oh-my-claudecode:executor","prompt_version":"P0_writer_pdf_v1.2","ts":"2026-04-26T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id":"ig34_p0242_a022","source":"SDTMIG_v3.4","page":242,"page_region":"bottom","parent_section":"§6.3.5.6 Laboratory Test Results (LB)","atom_type":"TABLE_ROW","verbatim":"| LBCOLSRT | Collected Summary Result Type | Char | (COLSTYP) | Record Qualifier | Used to indicate the type of collected summary result. This includes source summary results collected on a CRF or provided by an external vendor (e.g., central lab). If the summary result is derived by the sponsor | Perm |","heading_level":null,"sibling_index":null,"figure_ref":null,"cross_refs":[],"extracted_by":{"subagent_type":"oh-my-claudecode:executor","prompt_version":"P0_writer_pdf_v1.2","ts":"2026-04-26T00:00:00Z"}}
