{"atom_id": "ig34_p0248_a012", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 248, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.3.5.6 Laboratory Test Results (LB)", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "This example illustrates the use of the LBBDAGNT variable for a single agent. Note: More complex use cases may require additional concepts for complete modeling. In this simple target engagement assessment, the target protein analytes interact with the binding agent. The use of the word \"free\" in the descriptions of rows 2 and 4 does not refer to the naturally occurring hepatocyte growth factor receptors or epidermal growth factor receptors, but rather to the receptors not bound to the binding agent. Representing the binding agent shows that what is being measured is the portion of the target receptors not bound to the binding agent, not the concentration of the receptors at their natural state.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2", "ts": "2026-04-26T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0248_a013", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 248, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.3.5.6 Laboratory Test Results (LB)", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "Row 1:   Shows the total amount of HGFR, both soluble and bound, to the target \"ABC-8675309\".", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2", "ts": "2026-04-26T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0248_a014", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 248, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.3.5.6 Laboratory Test Results (LB)", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "Row 2:   Shows the amount of free HGFR not bound to the target \"ABC-8675309\" (i.e., a measure of the soluble analyte not bound to the target).", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2", "ts": "2026-04-26T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0248_a015", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 248, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "§6.3.5.6 Laboratory Test Results (LB)", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "Row 3:   Shows the total amount of EGFR, both soluble and bound, to the target \"ABC-8675309\".", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2", "ts": "2026-04-26T00:00:00Z"}}
