{"atom_id":"ig34_p0252_a001","source":"SDTMIG_v3.4","page":252,"page_region":"top","parent_section":"§6.3.5.7.1 Microbiology Specimen (MB)","atom_type":"LIST_ITEM","verbatim":"c. Culture characteristics covers concepts such as growth/no growth, colony quantification measures, colony color, colony morphology, and so on. Note that this does not include drug susceptibility testing, which is represented in the Microbiology Susceptibility (MS) domain.","cross_refs":[],"extracted_by":{"subagent_type":"oh-my-claudecode:writer","prompt_version":"P0_writer_pdf_v1.2","ts":"2026-04-27T08:15:00Z"}}
