{"atom_id": "ig34_p0273_a034", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 273, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "\u00a76.3.5.9.2 Pharmacokinetics Parameters (PP)", "atom_type": "HEADING", "verbatim": "Example 2", "heading_level": 7, "sibling_index": 2, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2", "ts": "2026-04-27T00:03:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0273_a035", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 273, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "\u00a76.3.5.9.2 Pharmacokinetics Parameters (PP)", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "This example shows various AUCs calculated using sponsor-defined formulas or the linear-log trapezoidal method.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2", "ts": "2026-04-27T00:03:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0273_a036", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 273, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "\u00a76.3.5.9.2 Pharmacokinetics Parameters (PP)", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "Rows 1-3: Show the \"AUC from T1 to T2\" measurements for Drug Parent (row 1), Drug Metabolite 1 (row 2) and Drug Metabolite 2 (row 3). These parameters are calculated using the LIN-LOG TRAPEZOIDAL METHOD which is in PPANMETH.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2", "ts": "2026-04-27T00:03:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0273_a037", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 273, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "\u00a76.3.5.9.2 Pharmacokinetics Parameters (PP)", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "Row 4: Shows the \"Ratio AUC\" measurement of Drug Metabolite 1 to Drug Parent. Instead of pre-corrdinating \"Ratio AUC of Drug Metabolite 1 to Drug Parent\" all into the PPTEST, PPANMETH is used to describe the numerator (Drug Metabolite 1) and the denominator (Drug Parent) values that contribute to the Ratio AUC calculation in PPTEST. This post-coordination approach liberates the PPTEST variable from having to house hyper-specific, pre-coordinated PK parameter values.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2", "ts": "2026-04-27T00:03:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0274_a001", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 274, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "\u00a76.3.5.9.2 Pharmacokinetics Parameters (PP)", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "Row 5: Shows the \"Ratio AUC\" measurement of Drug Metabolite 2 to Drug Metabolite 1. Note the PPTEST is Ratio AUC, whereas DRUG METABOLITE 2 TO METABOLITE 1 is in PPANMETH.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2", "ts": "2026-04-27T00:04:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0274_a002", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 274, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "\u00a76.3.5.9.2 Pharmacokinetics Parameters (PP)", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "Rows 6-7: Show AUC Infinity Obs and AUC Infinity Pred for the DRUG PARENT. Both are calculated using the LIN-LOG TRAPEZOIDAL METHOD which is in PPANMETH.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2", "ts": "2026-04-27T00:04:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0274_a003", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 274, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "\u00a76.3.5.9.2 Pharmacokinetics Parameters (PP)", "atom_type": "TABLE_HEADER", "verbatim": "Row | STUDYID | DOMAIN | USUBJID | PPSEQ | PPRFID | PPTESTCD | PPTEST | PPCAT | PPSCAT | PPORRES | PPORRESU | PPSTRESC | PPSTRESN | PPSTRESU | PPSPEC | PPANMETH | PPFAST | PPNOMDY | PPRFTDTC", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2", "ts": "2026-04-27T00:04:00Z"}}
