{"atom_id": "ig34_p0275_a013", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 275, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "\u00a76.3.5.9.3 Relating PP Records to PC Records", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Sponsors must document the concentrations used to calculate each parameter. This may be done in analysis dataset metadata or by documenting relationships between records in the Pharmacokinetics Parameters (PP) and Pharmacokinetics Concentrations (PC) datasets in a RELREC dataset (see Section 8.2, Relating Peer Records, and Section 8.3, Relating Datasets).", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": ["Section 8.2", "Section 8.3"], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.2", "ts": "2026-04-27T00:05:00Z"}}
